  // ── TRAIT-LIBRARY-EXPANSION §3b staged natural weapons ─────────────────────
  // New rungs of the staged weapon lines (claws/fangs/horns/tusks/venom/breath/talons/beak) plus the
  // §3e utility weapons. Same schema as the racial block above: hidden, amount 0, unbound unless a
  // limbmap part hosts them; binding runs through the granting condition's hostParts. Item-level
  // `bleedWound` = chance a landed open wound is unclottable (bleeds until dressed — the physical
  // successor of the retired `bloodletting` condition). Breath weapons carry `reach` (a spear-like
  // ranged strike; TODO: upgrade dragonfire's reach 3 to a true AoE cone) + `knockback`, deal FIRE
  // damage (a real burn wound) and proc the `burning` DoT.
