  // (Rings stay SINGLE-buff — the 7 elemental `<gem>_ring`s above. Two ring slots (`ring`/`ring2`) mean
  //  you wear two of them, so the weaker single buffs go on rings; the two-buff combos are amulet/crown
  //  only. No combo rings by design.)
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // §M ARCANE STAVES — INT-scaled (`arcane`) CHANNELED (`channeled`) ranged elemental weapons. They
  // fire on the ranged circuit (aim_accuracy/aim_speed/aim_range) but draw NO ammo: each shot pays
  // `staminaCost` as MANA (winded = out of mana) and the staff stays in hand. Element = the socketed
  // crystal (damageType fire/frost/lightning → fire/cold/lightning resistance); wood = the shaft.
  // Two tiers per element mirror iron→steel: T1 (Runecarver's Bench, cut crystal) → T2 (Attunement
  // Altar, attuned crystal + gold; also grants the attuned gem's passive buff while wielded). §Q quality
