  // ── PRODUCTION-CHAIN-II §L — Bulk Logistics ──────────────────────────────────────────────
  // `wheel` is the crafted intermediate. wheelbarrow/handcart are two-handed `tool`s: equipping one
  // fills the hands (mainHand) — so the pawn can't wield a weapon (Combat falls back to unarmed) —
  // and grants a big `inventoryBonus`, raising the SAME carry budget belts/baskets use (no separate
  // bulk pool). Self-weight is low: the wheels bear the load, the pusher just steers. Overloading
  // still costs move-speed via the load→encumbrance term in PawnService.getMoveSpeed.
